          "reviewBody": "NOTE: REVIEW MADE BEFORE SUNSHINE AQUISITION, DONT TAKE INTO ACCOUNT\n\nVery hectic school, they make fuss over anything and everything,For example, if you bring lollipop to school and they find it, instead of saying something like eat it in free time, they cruelly take it away .It also has Horrible  food, very horrible school.",
