            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "SSM was one of the best schools in chennai. Unlike other schools they do not loot parents and the food served to kids are also of good quality. Very systematic in teaching kids without overloading. Kids will enjoy studying here. Best school with Montessori system of education to start schooling but unfortunately things have changed now.Think twice about your kids future.",
          "publisher": {
