          "reviewBody": "Recently Enquired for KG admissions. Fee is 69000 per year inclusive of all. But the donation is 100000rs which is non refundable deposit which should be paid within 15 days from the date of submitting the application.. Many international school fees are lesser than this amount. Management should think twice before asking this much fees..",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
